verbose_text: Decreased frequencies of DKA at onset of disease have been reported from Finland between 1982 and 2001, with a decrease from 22.4 to 15.2% in children 0-15 years of age and a decrease from 32.1 to 17.7% in children with onset before the age of 5 years.
